service.name: Low Income Health Care Card
service.description: Low Income Health Care Card also known as a Low Income Card (LIC) a  Low Income Health Care Card entitles the customer to Commonwealth health concessions such as pharmaceutical benefits. It may also provide access to a limited range of State and Local Government concessions such as health, household, educational, recreational, and transport. Many private companies also offer concessions to Low Income Health Care Card holders.
